<li><strong><strong>Friday, July 18 at 5:00pm (PDT)<br />
</strong></strong></p>
<p><div id="attachment_1858" style="width: 250px" class="wp-caption alignright"><a href="http://nvcopblock.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ChalkPoliceStateFlyerF.jpg"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1858" src="http://nvcopblock.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/ChalkPoliceStateFlyerF-240x300.jpg" alt="ChalkPoliceStateFlyerF 240x300 Chalk the Police State (July 18th)   Updated List of Cities" width="240" height="300" title="Chalk the Police State (July 18th)   Updated List of Cities" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">This is can be used as a template for other cities&#8217; flyers.</p></div></li>
