</ul>
<h2><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Seattle, WA.</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>FaceBook event page: <span class="_6lc fwb"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/678427472238962/?ref=4" data-ft="{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;q&quot;}">Seattle Chalk-in against Police Brutality!</a></span></li>
<li><strong>Friday, July 18 at 4:00pm (PDT)<br />
</strong></li>
<li><span class="_6s_"><span class="_5inl" data-hover="tooltip" data-tooltip-display="overflow">5th Ave and Cherry St</span></span></li>
<li><span class="_6s_"><span class="_5inl" data-hover="tooltip" data-tooltip-display="overflow"> Seattle, WA</span></span></li>
</ul>
<h2><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Kansas City, KS.</span></h2>
<p>Hosted by<span class="fcg"> <a id="js_14" class="profileLink" href="https://www.facebook.com/KCKCopBlock" data-ft="{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;k&quot;}" data-hovercard="/ajax/hovercard/page.php?id=297273257076773&amp;extragetparams=%7B%22directed_target_id%22%3A143037152533300%7D">KCK Cop Block</a></span></p>
<ul>
<li>FaceBook event page: <span class="_6lc fwb"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/266410560218030/?ref=4" data-ft="{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;q&quot;}">Chalk the Police State in Solidarity with the Victims of Police Brutality, Repression, and Murder- Kansas City</a></span></li>
<li><strong>Friday, July 18 at 12:00pm (CDT)</strong></li>
<li><span class="_6s_"><span class="_6s_"><span class="_5ini fsm fwn fcg"><a class="_5inl" href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Wyandotte-County-Courthouse/144788882247839" data-hovercard="/ajax/hovercard/page.php?id=144788882247839">Wyandotte County Courthouse</a> <span class="_6s_"><span class="_5ini fsm fwn fcg"><span class="_6s_"><span class="_5inl" data-hover="tooltip" data-tooltip-display="overflow">(click for</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>
<div id="attachment_1859" style="width: 239px" class="wp-caption alignright"><a href="http://nvcopblock.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/OlyChalkPoliceStateFlyerF.jpg"><img class="size-medium wp-image-1859" src="http://nvcopblock.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/OlyChalkPoliceStateFlyerF-229x300.jpg" alt="OlyChalkPoliceStateFlyerF 229x300 Chalk the Police State (July 18th)   Updated List of Cities" width="229" height="300" title="Chalk the Police State (July 18th)   Updated List of Cities" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">The &#8220;Chalk the Police State&#8221; Flyer for Olympia, Wa.</p></div>
